  <p>An HTML parser written in Common Lisp.</p>

  <h3>About</h3>

  <p>
    Closure HTML was written
    by <a href="http://www.stud.uni-karlsruhe.de/~unk6/">Gilbert
    Baumann</a> as part of the Closure web browser.  It was first
    converted into a stand-alone installation by Ignas MikalajÅ«nas, and
    finally rebuilt for use with the Closure browser by
    <a href="mailto:david@lichteblau.com">David Lichteblau</a> under its
    current name.
  </p>
  <p>
    It available under an MIT-style license.
